Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我研究了萨道克那本旧书\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was sifting through Sadoc's old book.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,毛脚族很久以前就走过这条路了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harfoots must've journeyed this way a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,伊斯塔尔一定会屈服在我手下 不然的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Istar will surrender to me, because if he doesn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我就杀了他称之为朋友的半身人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will slaughter the halflings he calls friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,诺瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要往山脊线去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Were you headed for the ridgeline?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,幸存者会在扎营处等我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The survivors will be waiting for us where we made camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,–还有我父亲 –你可能错过他们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- My father, too. - I think you may have missed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,–你也在找家人吗  –我未婚夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You hoping to find kin as well? My betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他有你一半坚强 我敢肯定他会撑过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he's even half as strong as you, I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我没你想的那么坚强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not so strong as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之间曾有的关联 现在也化为灰烬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything you were to me, is ashes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我是觉得 我们没必要再交谈了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So for my part, we don't ever need to speak again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你真想找回你的马\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}D'you really want your horse back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,–你知道它在哪  –今晚这里见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You know where he is? - Meet me here. Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,小鬼 你那么晚在外面干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doin' out here in the dark, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有埋伏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an ambush!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.37,0:01:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,领主大人 准备工作就快完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Preparations are nearly complete, Lord-father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要再次开战吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Must we go to war again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,除非确定索隆彻底消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll never truly be safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们永远不会真正安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until we've made certain Sauron is no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,自从戴上这枚戒指 我能感知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since the wearing of this Ring, I have perceived
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不可见世界的闪现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}glimpses of the unseen world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们送去给凯勒布林博的消息 都没有回音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our letters to Celebrimbor have all gone unanswered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心索隆已经潜入埃瑞吉安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I fear Sauron may be in Eregion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,至高王同意我带一小队人马过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The High King has consented to send me and a small party there,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.70,0:01:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,确定凯勒布林博和埃瑞吉安很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to ensure Celebrimbor and his city are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔隆德的任务不是加入你的阵容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond's task is not to join your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而是领导阵容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But to lead it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}指环王:力量之戒\N第二季第四集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs21}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,凯勒布林博还是没回复...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still no word from Celebrimbor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果走阿克萨桥 不到730公里就能到埃瑞吉安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we take the Axa Bridge, Eregion is just under 150 leagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要一名弓箭手 两名剑士 相信你能推荐好人选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We shall need an archer, two swordsmen. I trust you can recommend a set.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,相信 我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定这样好吗 指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you certain that's wise, commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在至高王的催促下 我同意任命你为第二指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At the High King's urging, I agreed to appointment you as first lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你认为有失你的身份 我会另择他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you deem that duty beneath you, I will choose another.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,–是的 –什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes. -"Yes" what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我能推荐 一名弓箭手和两名剑士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I can recommend an archer and two swordsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还要带谁去 指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who else shall we take with us, commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,闪电\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何世俗力量能办到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No earthly force could do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是索隆的杰作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the work of Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,坎尼尔 还有哪条路能走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Camnir. What other paths might we take?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要绕过去的话 我们要么往北\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To circumvent it, we shall either have to turn due north,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,多花两周时间...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}adding two weeks to our journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不然呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不然往南 穿越图林戈沙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We go south, through the Hills of Tyrn Gorthad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,到埃瑞吉安会快很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which will get us to Eregion much faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有邪恶之物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is evil in those hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,存在久远 充满恶意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ancient, and filled with malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,索隆故意要我们走那条路 我们必须走另一条\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sauron means for us to go that way. We must go another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大敌肯定两条路都监视着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Enemy is doubtless watching both roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,看这坍塌 我们要更快赶到凯勒布林博那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This collapse makes it more critical than ever to reach Celebrimbor at speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,万一走进陷阱我们哪都到不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We won't reach anywhere at speed if we walk into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,往南走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We go south.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥官 我得反对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander, I must protest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到你的意见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your opinion on the matter has been heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了 第二指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Opinion heard, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们往南走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We go south.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会听从那小玩意的建议 你也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This company will not take counsel from that trinket, nor will you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不能遵守这些条件 你现在就回林顿去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you cannot abide by those terms, you will leave now and return to Lindon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,–我是很想 –那为何不走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I should like to. - Then why do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不想看到有人送命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I do not wish to see any of this company slain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,包括你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,诺瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,诺瑞 波比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori! Poppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 你有看到两个半身人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pardon me. I don't suppose you've seen a pair of halflings come this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你找到羔羊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See you found the goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我要找的...不是羔羊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It wasn't... quite what I was searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你要找的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there's what you're searchin' for
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你也找到了 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and there's what you find, now, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,欢乐咚 快活咚 敲响叮叮咚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey dol, merry dol Ring a dong dillow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,白蛉草地飞 蜜蜂柳树转\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sandflies in the grass Bees around the willow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你的山丘上方有星星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are some stars above your hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,山丘上方常有星星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stars above most 'ills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我朋友在找这些星星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But my friends and I were looking for these stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来希望...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had hoped that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My apologies, j-just a moment--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,歌唱那太阳 星星 月亮与轻雾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of sun, stars Moon and mist
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雨水与云天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rain and cloudy weather
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,魔杖...当然了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The branch... of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. It must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:10:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,波比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,–有看到他吗  –谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}D'you see him? - Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你说咧 我们的朋友 那天杀的异乡人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who d'you think? Our friend, the bleedin' Stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,先别管他在哪 我们在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never mind where's he, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,诺瑞 快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 应该是甩掉他们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think, I think we lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你们哪来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where'd you lot come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你又是哪来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的脑袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,–我住这 –毛脚族住这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Live here. - Harfoots live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,毛脚族是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's an Harfoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you are--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是无名仔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你不可能是“无名仔”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you can't be "Nobody."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都这么叫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well... That's what everybody calls me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果大家都叫你无名仔 没人叫你某某某吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If everybody calls you Nobody, doesn't anybody call you somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈叫我梅里麦克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, my mum calls me Merimac.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是波比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Poppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我是诺瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Nori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你的水从哪弄来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where'd you get that water from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,–小声一点 –偷来的 对不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep your voice down. You stole it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,从大家伙那口井偷来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You stole it from that well. From the big folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,–你去哪  –没有啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But-- Where are you going? Uh, nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,带我们一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take us with ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 村子严禁外人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, sorry, no outsiders in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,村子 什么村子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Village? What village?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 没有村子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No village! There's no village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,给我听好 无名仔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen here, Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要么让我们跟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Either we're coming with you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不然就告发你 偷水贼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or I will turn you in myself this moment, water-thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你们待会儿会见到阿古 我们的领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're about to meet The Gund, our dwell-leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,想要她考虑收留你们 要遵守四条规定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you want her to even think about takin' you in, there's four rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,第一 不要直视她的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One, never look her in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,第二 永远距离她三步远\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}B, always stand three steps back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,第四 不管怎样 千万不要叫她阿古\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Four, don't, ever, ever, no matter what, call her "The Gund."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,–了解 –了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Got it. - Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,规定是三条还四条\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was that three rules or four?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我没认真听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't really paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 好好玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Off you go, have fun now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊 那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为有阳光照射\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's 'cause it's had the sunshine on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,看那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 很新鲜 可以剥皮了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice, fresh batch, ready to peel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,–大帽子 跟我的一样  –跟爸的一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Big hat, like mine! Like Dad's!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,毛脚族住在洞穴里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harfoots, livin' in holes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,–感觉怪怪的 –因为我们不是毛脚族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It doesn't seem natural. -That's 'cause we're not Harfoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是壮躯族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're Stoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,壮躯族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stoors?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事带她们来干嘛 没有人那么笨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What were you thinkin', bringin' 'em here? Nobody's that stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她们需要一个藏身处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They needed a place to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎样 沙漠里有魔鬼要抓她们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, with half the devils in the desert searchin' for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小鬼 要是秃鹰吞了你脑袋 肯定倒退飞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boy, if we put your brains in a vulture, it'd fly backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,别对他那么凶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be nicer to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在顶撞我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you talkin' back-sass to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那是第四条规定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, that was the fourth rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,给我一个好理由不把你们丢出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me one good reason why I shouldn't feed you leg, limb, and joint
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,送给那些追杀你们的高德林人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to those Gaudrim hunting you out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说啊 我听听看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on, plead your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我淌过河流 越过高山\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have walked across rivers, and mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,穿过沙漠 帮助我的朋友寻找他的天命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and deserts to help my friend find his destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他的天命可能左右着 这世界的命运 包括你们...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one the fate of the world may well depend on, yours included--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我说给我一个好理由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said one good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你那个朋友 他是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This friend of yours, who is he, anyways?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,–他是个巨人 –巨人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's a giant. - A giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,–什么 像精灵吗  –比精灵更大尾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What, like an Elf? - Bigger than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他是超大只精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So he's a great big Grand-Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not an Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个巫师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这片天空下唯一的巫师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the only wizard under these skies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是黑巫师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is the Dark Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最不需要的朋友就是他的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the last friend we need is a friend of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,把她们绑起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tie 'em up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什么鬼 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? What? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,放开她 黑巫师是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? Let her go. What Dark Wizard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,伊斯塔尔变得 比我们预期的更加强大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Istar is already much more powerful than we had anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他凭空召唤出沙尘暴 杀了我两名手下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He conjured a sandstorm from thin air that killed two of my men,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在往北去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He makes his way north now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,往...那隐士的方向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Towards... the hermit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那两个半身人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what of the halflings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在沙漠搜索 她们躲不了太久的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are scouring the desert even now. They will not evade us for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我以性命发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I swear my life on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,高德林人 你要不是很笨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are either very foolish, Gaudrim,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就是很勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or very brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你专心处理那两个毛脚族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let the Harfoots be your sole concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,伊斯塔尔交给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will see to the Istar myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再放他出来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let him out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不该醒来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should not be wakin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,吃土壤 挖深点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eat earth. Dig deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,喝点水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drink water, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,去睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who... Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没人叫我什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Been awhile since I've been called much of anythin',
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,以前在柳条河一带 大家都叫我邦巴迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but back in the Withywindle, folk used to call me Bombadil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆邦巴迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom Bombadil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳西沉啦 快要摸黑啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Down west sinks the sun Soon you will be gropin'
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别害羞了 金莓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be bashful now, Goldberry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,夜影来临时 家门为你开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the night-shadows fall Then the door will open
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经很努力洗你的脏袍子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've done such as I can with your filthy robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,洗洗手 洗洗脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, clean your hands, wash your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,过来跟我一起烤火吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then come join me by the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,外面还有其他人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is, uh... Is somebody out there with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像听到一个女人在唱歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought I heard a woman singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,女人 什么女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Woman? What woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没有其他人在吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is no one else here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你在啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is, I think you are. Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh... Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 你本来希望 在星星下面找到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, what was it that you were hopin' to find under those stars of yours, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不会是老汤姆吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Certainly not old Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,希望找到我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was hoping to find my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,星星又懂什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shows what stars know, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,它们就是新来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Newcomers, that's what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,某一年还很暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One year, it's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,下一年 你抬头看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The next, you look up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,发现一大片小眼睛往下盯着你看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's a sea of tiny eyes lookin' down at ya, a-watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,它们以为自己无所不知 但不过就是新来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, they think they know everythin', but newcomers. Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还嫩得很\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still newcomers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你还不知道我名字吗  那是唯一的答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you know my name yet? That's the only answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我才想问你是什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me, who are you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,孤身一人 无名无姓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}alone, yourself, and nameless?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你年轻 我已经老了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you are young, and I am old.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是个最老之人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eldest, that's what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,“最老之人”是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean, "Eldest"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是最老之人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eldest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,记住我的话 朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mark my words, friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在河流和树木出现前 汤姆就在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom was there before the river and the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆记得第一滴雨滴和第一颗橡实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom remembers the first raindrop and the first acorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他看过星空之下没有恐惧的黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knew the dark under the stars when it was fearless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这里曾一片青葱翠绿 现在全是沙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This whole place used to be green. Now, it's all sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我还得亲眼目睹才敢相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had to come see for myself to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,连鸟鸣声都受影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even the birdsong isn't wholly untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,连外面那棵老铁木也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even your tree out there. Old Man Ironwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为它...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought it--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他或许愿意借我一根树枝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He... might be able to, lend me a branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该问问他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, well you should've tried askin' him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,放轻松 伊尔温 放轻松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy, Iarwain. Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这种...魔法 你能教我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This... magic. Can you teach it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,教你 这里有什么好学的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Teach you? What's to learn way out 'ere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你能控制树 控制风和火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wield power over trees, over wind and fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像它们属于你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wield it, as if it belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:22:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,天地万物都属于它们自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All things belong each to themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.79,0:22:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你属于你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just as you belong to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那你能教我该怎么使用魔杖吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then, might you teach me how to wield a staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,巫师的魔杖就像名字一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A wizard's staff is like a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,本来就属于你 你只要证明自己配得上它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's yours to wield already, if you prove yourself worthy of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天证明了你还不够格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You showed today that you're not. Yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能变得够格 我们很快就会知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whether you can become so, well, we shall soon discover.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这些星星下要找的不是魔杖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was never meant to find a staff under these stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而是你 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was meant to find you. Wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什么声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.87,0:22:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有伴了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.29,0:23:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要追杀我和我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do they hunt me, and my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是第一个 在我火堆旁吃蜂蜜的伊斯塔尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are not the first Istar who's eaten honey by my fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很多年前有另一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Years ago, there was another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,黑巫师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Dark Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他后来怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What became of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.62,0:23:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他也曾跟你一样想掌控魔法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once, he sought to control magic, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他掌控了大部分鲁恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, he controls much of Rh?n.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.79,0:23:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但仍然渴望得到更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But still, he hungers for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.83,0:23:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你担心他的邪恶会蔓延\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You believe his evil will spread?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,除非有比他更强大的盟友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not without an ally far more powerful even than himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:23:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,索隆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要是这两团烈火合而为一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If these two flames combine into one,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,中洲将无尽燃烧 直到灰飞烟灭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there will be no end to burnin', till all Middle-earth is ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.45,0:24:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你能阻止吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老汤姆是个漫游者 不是战士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old Tom's a wanderer, not a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.66,0:24:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,伟大事迹要交付命定之人手上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great deeds are left to the hands they were placed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.75,0:24:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我要趁睡莲生长之时采摘它们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I shall gather lilies, while yet they grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.16,0:24:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.54,0:24:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,交付我手上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.83,0:24:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我的使命是阻止这场烈火吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it my task to stop the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.66,0:24:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的使命是面对索隆吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it my task to face Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.91,0:25:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你的使命 是面对他们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your task... is to face them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.50,0:25:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我等着你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.54,0:25:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.00,0:25:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,图林戈沙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tyrn Gorthad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.50,0:25:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人类称为古冢岗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Known to Men as the Barrow-downs.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.91,0:25:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在远古时代 这里是他们的领主和国王安息的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In ancient days, this was where they laid their lords and kings to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.66,0:26:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没有安息的气息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel no rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.12,0:26:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就连树木也显得不安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even the trees seem ill at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.66,0:26:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不用怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fear not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.58,0:26:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,死人构不成威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dead Men are no threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.33,0:26:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,继续走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.20,0:26:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,四体僵冷 刺骨入心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cold be hand and heart and bone
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.04,0:26:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,岩洞长眠寒似冰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And cold be sleep under stone
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.75,0:26:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有一瞬间 我好像听到...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For a moment, I thought I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.70,0:26:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,听到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.87,0:26:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.62,0:27:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来像是一首歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was almost like a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.00,0:27:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,或是一首歌的回忆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or the memory of a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.04,0:27:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.25,0:27:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这些护甲出自林顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their barding is from Lindon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.83,0:27:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,至高王派了人去警告凯勒布林博\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The King sent a dispatch to warn Celebrimbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.16,0:27:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是这人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This dispatch?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.91,0:27:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要赶快离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must go from this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.45,0:27:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,–戴莫尔  –抓住我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Daemor! - Hold on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.75,0:27:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,别放手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.08,0:28:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,四体僵冷 刺骨入心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cold old be hand and heart and bone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.58,0:28:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,岩洞长眠寒似冰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And cold be sleep under stone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.50,0:28:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如今墓穴长眠罢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never more to wake on stony bed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.91,0:28:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,直到日月陨落不再明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never, till the Sun fails and the Moon is dead
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.12,0:28:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,黑风吹袭 星辰将晦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the black wind the stars shall die
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.54,0:28:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,准备迎战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prepare yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.58,0:28:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.45,0:28:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,古冢尸妖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Barrow-wights.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.70,0:29:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.66,0:29:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,箭不虚发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still your arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.20,0:29:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的武器对他们没用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're impervious to our weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.62,0:29:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,撑住 跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold fast. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.45,0:29:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.75,0:29:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,–帮我打开 –什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Help me open it. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.83,0:29:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.87,0:29:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,第二指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.12,0:30:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.62,0:30:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.45,0:30:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,根据传说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}According to lore,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.66,0:30:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只有埋葬他们的刀剑 才能让他们安息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}only the blades with which they were buried will return such creatures to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.00,0:30:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但这些人已经埋葬千年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the Men buried here have been entombed for over a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.45,0:30:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看来有东西唤醒了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it is safe to say that something has awoken them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.95,0:30:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.08,0:30:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.62,0:30:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,唤醒了邪恶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Awakening evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.33,0:30:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,整个中洲的邪恶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Across all of Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.70,0:30:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,西奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo! Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.66,0:30:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,–西奥  –西奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Theo! Theo! Theo! Theo! Theo! - Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.00,0:31:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,西奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.08,0:31:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,西奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.04,0:31:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,–西奥  –西奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Theo! -Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.00,0:31:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把武器都留了下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They left all their weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.37,0:31:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对野人来说 斧头比金子还值钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To a Wildman, an axe-head is worth more than gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.04,0:31:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没把武器带走太奇怪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strange, they did not take it with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.79,0:31:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大家过来 我们继续\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come, all of you. We move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.62,0:31:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这边 来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This way. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.41,0:31:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要折磨自己 努曼诺尔人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not torture yourself, Númenórean.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.62,0:31:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,西奥经历过更糟的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo has survived far worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.08,0:31:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他会活下来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He will weather this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.37,0:31:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,西奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.75,0:31:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,西奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.41,0:32:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,西奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.70,0:32:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的 往这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You there. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.12,0:32:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,突袭他们营地吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I say we raid their camps.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.29,0:32:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样会挑起战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'd be starting a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.00,0:32:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,已经开战了 臭海人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're already at war, Sea-folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.12,0:32:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我所看到的 我不认为是凡人做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I saw, I do not believe was done by mortal Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.37,0:32:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不是人 是野兽 有必要还会吃人肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're not Men. They're animals. They'd eat human flesh if they had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.45,0:33:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每浪费一分钟 西奥就多一分危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every minute we waste is another Theo's still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.37,0:33:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要继续找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've got to keep searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.66,0:33:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可以去伊斯菲尔谷看看 听说野人在那里扎营\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We could canvass Eastfield Glen. Whispers are, Wildmen camp there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.91,0:33:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.00,0:33:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,最好往北看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd do better to look north.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.20,0:33:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why north?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.45,0:33:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我花了好几个星期 在这片大地寻找我爱的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've spent weeks searching these lands, lookin' for loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.08,0:33:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,北方那片森林很古老\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That part of the forest is old.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.00,0:33:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那里肯定有野人 甚至更可怕的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Promise you, there are Wildmen there, and worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.70,0:33:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有道理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.00,0:33:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,阿隆迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arondir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.25,0:33:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别浪费大白天了 收集饮水和粮食\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's not waste any daylight. Gather water and provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.62,0:33:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,动起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.37,0:33:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.54,0:33:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你漏了一个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You missed a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.83,0:34:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.75,0:34:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你们岛上应该从来不缺水吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fancy you never want for water on your island.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.16,0:34:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 努曼诺尔家家户户都有水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. In Númenor, we have water in most of our homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.41,0:34:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真想看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.54,0:34:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你未婚夫肯定也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wager your betrothed would too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.66,0:34:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,该继续前进了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We ought to keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.20,0:34:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.41,0:34:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丝翠 你说你跟野人相处过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You say you spent time among the Wildmen, Estrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.45,0:34:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.62,0:34:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我没跟他们相处 我躲起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, I wasn't exactly among them. I was hidin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.54,0:34:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,–他们有伤害你吗  –阿隆迪尔 你干嘛...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Did they ever do you harm? - Arondir, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.83,0:34:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我问是因为我发现你脖子上有伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I ask because I noticed a wound on your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.29,0:34:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来是最近弄伤的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks to be recent.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.62,0:34:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我自己弄的 我在火边睡着了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. That was my fault. I, um... fell asleep by the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.83,0:34:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该熄灭的 但那晚太冷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should've put it out, but the night was cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.91,0:34:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是我太蠢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was foolish of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.08,0:34:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们难免都会做蠢事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all do foolish things sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.95,0:34:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是在绝望的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Especially in moments of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.45,0:35:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丝翠 那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Estrid, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.29,0:35:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,自己烧的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Self-burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.91,0:35:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,野人以此隐藏阿达尔印记\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Wildmen do it to hide the Mark of Adar.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.20,0:35:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是她跟你进来 在入口处就会逮到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We would have caught her at the gate had she not come in with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.20,0:35:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说她是野人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's a Wildman?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.12,0:35:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她是他们的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.25,0:35:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她会带我们找到其他野人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And she's going to lead us to all the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.08,0:35:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你本来打算怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.45,0:35:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,攻击我 抢走我的马\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stab me? Take my horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.91,0:35:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was that it? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.45,0:35:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,后来你发现我是努曼诺尔人 想到更好的主意 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you saw I was a Númenórean. Had a better idea, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.75,0:35:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直在利用我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were using me all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.95,0:35:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本没未婚夫吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wager you don't even have a betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.58,0:36:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,–你宁愿我死在魔多  –不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Would you rather I died in Mordor? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.91,0:36:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.70,0:36:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.41,0:36:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be still.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.75,0:36:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.41,0:36:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,西奥根本不是被人类抓走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo was not taken by Men at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.70,0:37:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.54,0:37:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小胖醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well-fed's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.37,0:37:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.87,0:37:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,外面那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.41,0:37:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 不管是什么 一定很大只\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't know yet. But whatever they are, they're big.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.16,0:37:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小心脚下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.95,0:37:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,能用手的话会比较好平衡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might be easier to balance if I had use of my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.95,0:38:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,也比较好逃跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And easier to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.95,0:38:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这样没人逃得掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one could escape in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.29,0:38:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我解开吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, unlock me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.54,0:38:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.70,0:38:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,别动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be still.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.08,0:38:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我说我可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.87,0:38:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,手给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.87,0:38:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.54,0:38:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,拉我起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lift me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.91,0:38:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要沉下去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.54,0:39:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,刚那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.54,0:39:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,世界深处多的是无名之物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are nameless things in the deep places of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.58,0:40:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这一个...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.25,0:40:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们称之为“晚餐”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we shall call "supper."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.75,0:40:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我跟村里的长老商量过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, I've conferred with the village elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.75,0:40:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,日出时把你们两个赶出去 抱歉 但壮躯族优先\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You two are to be cast out at sunrise. Sorry, but Stoors must come first.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.87,0:40:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说 换作是他...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Truth is, he was in your place...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.45,0:40:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,换作是萨道克也会这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc likely would've done the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.29,0:40:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,萨道克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.66,0:40:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的寻路人 他叫萨道克布罗斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our trail-finder. He was called Sadoc Burrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.54,0:40:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你们领袖叫萨道克布罗斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc Burrows was your leader's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.87,0:40:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信你 只是想确认一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just so's we're both working with a full bushel, I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.66,0:40:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你看这个只是想充分确认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm only showin' you this to make good and sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.66,0:40:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,确认什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.12,0:41:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,相传在古代有个壮躯族人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Story goes, in ancient days, there was a Stoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.70,0:41:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我们其他人很不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wasn't like the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.79,0:41:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,据说有天晚上他梦到一个地方 那里有一望无际的清凉溪流\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They say he dreamed one night of a place, with endless streams of cold water
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.83,0:41:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,绵延起伏的柔软山丘 不用一个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and rollin' hills so soft, a family could dig a hole
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.50,0:41:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一家人就能挖个洞住进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and live in it in less than a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.91,0:41:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他称那里为“苏萨”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He called it "the S?zat."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.62,0:41:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有一年他带着一群追随者出发寻找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Struck out one year with a caravan of followers to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.70,0:41:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,承诺等他找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Promised, when he did,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.33,0:41:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,会派人回来带我们大家过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he'd send someone back to gather the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.45,0:41:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我们最后一次听到 罗里马斯布罗斯这名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that was the last any of us ever heard of Rorimas Burrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.79,0:41:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,波比的行脚之歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poppy's walkin' song.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.79,0:41:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,毛脚族来过这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harfoots have been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.83,0:42:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你的村子 你的家乡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your kind's home, where you come from,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.29,0:42:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像这样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}does it look like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.54,0:42:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是回来带我们大家去苏萨的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you come back here to lead us all to the S?zat?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.00,0:42:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我想...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.50,0:42:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,罗里马斯从未找到苏萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rorimas never found the S?zat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.12,0:42:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,过了好久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And after a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.66,0:42:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直在流浪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we just kept wanderin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.20,0:42:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't have a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.29,0:42:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,骑马人来了 大家伙 这边走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The riders sighted. Big folk. Comin' this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.79,0:43:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,各位大驾光临...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To what do we owe the pleasure of--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.41,0:43:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,毛脚族人 在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Harfoots, where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.16,0:43:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这片沙漠我们唯一知道的半身人 就只有壮躯族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only halflings we know about in this desert are Stoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.58,0:43:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我们为何戴面具吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know why we wear these masks?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.45,0:44:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,敢反抗黑巫师 等他亲自过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Defy the Dark Wizard and, when we return with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.50,0:44:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就会知道答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you will find out for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.08,0:44:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你认为这戒指在欺骗我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you believe this Ring is deceiving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.58,0:44:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但我相信它在指引我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I believe it is guiding me,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.12,0:44:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,跟随指引可能是我们 通往胜利的唯一道路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that following it may be our only path to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.00,0:44:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,万一胜利的代价变得太大呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there no point at which the cost of victory becomes too great?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.04,0:44:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还没到那个地步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have yet to reach that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.45,0:44:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么就不害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How does that not terrify you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.04,0:44:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为索隆统治世界所带来的苦难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because the suffering of a world ruled by Sauron
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.87,0:45:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,更让我害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}terrifies me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.70,0:45:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都能感觉到 但戴上戒指后 我能清楚看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have always felt it. But with this Ring, I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.45,0:45:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果无法完成眼前的任务 我们将失去一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything we stand to lose if we fail in the task before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.66,0:45:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲预见了 有一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father foresaw that, one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.41,0:45:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,凯勒布林博的命运会掌握在我手里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Celebrimbor's life would be in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.83,0:45:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我会选择我该走的路 拚尽全力加以保护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will choose the path I must to give me the best hope of protecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.87,0:45:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,保护最脆弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Protecting that which is most fragile,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.00,0:45:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,最珍贵的东西是所有精灵的使命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}most dear, is a task entrusted to all Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.75,0:45:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这个使命尚未完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And one that is not yet complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.20,0:46:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对还会有更多痛苦的牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I promise you, there will be more painful sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.70,0:46:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.50,0:46:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,答应我 埃尔隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Promise me, Elrond,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.95,0:46:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你会把消灭索隆放在第一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you will put opposing Sauron above all other considerations.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.75,0:46:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至优先于我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.95,0:46:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会答应被戒指左右之人任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will make no promise whose asking is borne of that Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.70,0:46:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但我发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I swear to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.37,0:46:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,消灭索隆会是第一要务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}defeating Sauron will come first.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.33,0:46:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至优先于你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.58,0:46:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥官 抱歉打扰 我们听到鼓声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, commander, we heard drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.66,0:47:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是手铐的钥匙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that the key to the manacles?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.62,0:47:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他是要让你决定用不用吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Believe he meant for you to decide whether or not to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.87,0:47:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.12,0:48:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.08,0:48:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不 伊熙尔杜 那个...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Isildur, y'see...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.66,0:48:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,像我这种人不会得到原谅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgiveness doesn't come to folk like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.75,0:48:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们迟早会赶我走 你很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sooner or later, they'll cast me out, you know they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.33,0:48:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让他们这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.25,0:48:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让他们赶你走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't let them cast you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.62,0:48:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,放下剑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put down the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.79,0:48:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丝翠 放下剑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Estrid, drop the sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.25,0:48:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丝翠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Estrid!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.16,0:49:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.08,0:49:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是大绿林的阿隆迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am Arondir, of the Greenwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.04,0:49:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾拿斧头砍过树木吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hast thou ever touched axe to wooded life?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.33,0:49:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很痛苦 但...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To my great pain, I have, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.33,0:49:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.20,0:49:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是为了砍下树木\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is not for felling trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.20,0:50:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那是为了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does it fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.62,0:50:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,奥克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Orcs.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.66,0:50:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,退后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.16,0:50:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有一支...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was an...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.16,0:50:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,奥克大军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}an army of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.91,0:50:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一边行进 一边屠杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maiming and murdering as they marched.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.12,0:50:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看到他们干的好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We saw what they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.62,0:50:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你们才来这 才这么生气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that why you're here? Why you're so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.29,0:50:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喷溅的树液和燃烧的树枝 从远处呼唤我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The spilling sap and burning branch called to us from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.83,0:50:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...我们来得太迟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But... we were too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.58,0:50:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,大军 多久以前的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An army? How long ago was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.66,0:50:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,冬花从这些树还小就滋养他们长大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Winterbloom nourished many of those trees from seed and sprout.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.87,0:50:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别要她再多说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not ask her to speak more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.83,0:50:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们跟他们没两样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are no different from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.33,0:51:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,连根拔起 砍断树枝 劈开树干 坏事做尽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Disemboweling, and uprooting, branch-breakers and trunk-splitters, all!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.41,0:51:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We would seek...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.00,0:51:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,为造成的伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your forgiveness...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.04,0:51:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,诚挚恳求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.50,0:51:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的原谅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...we have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.54,0:51:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅需要时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgiveness takes an age.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.16,0:52:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要等雨水洗去土壤的沉痛记忆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rain washing clear the long memory of soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.29,0:52:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,新鲜树皮覆盖陈旧伤疤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}New bark, covering old scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.66,0:52:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在这段时间里 我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in all that time, I promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.45,0:52:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会确保这片森林平静祥和\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we will see to it that the trees of this wood are left in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.20,0:52:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道什么意思吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think they know what peace is?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.08,0:52:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,夜晚暴风雨过后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is what comes after the night storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.00,0:52:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,黎明宁静 鸟儿苏醒那个片刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when the dawn is silent, and the birds awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.70,0:52:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在山脉拔地而起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have tended this forest
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.20,0:52:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,切割大地之前 我们就在照料这片森林了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}since before the mountains rose up and divided it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.79,0:53:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那时这里唯一的声音 只有苔藓沐浴阳光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the only sound here was the light upon the moss...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.25,0:53:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,西奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.33,0:53:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,和树叶呼吸起伏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the breathing of the leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.58,0:53:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我们知道平静祥和什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. We know peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.50,0:53:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丝翠 是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Estrid? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.87,0:53:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丝翠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Estrid? Estrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.25,0:53:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哈根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hagen?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.50,0:53:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,–我以为... –我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What... I thought you... - So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.75,0:53:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信真的是你 看看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't believe you're here. Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.62,0:54:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你来救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for coming for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.62,0:54:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.70,0:54:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你信守承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for keepin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.70,0:54:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我要信守另一个承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I must keep another.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.87,0:54:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,奥克不断前进 我要跟上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Orcs are on the move. I must follow the trail where it leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.62,0:54:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定有机会再次对上阿达尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps have another chance to confront Adar.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.70,0:54:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要的话你可以跟我一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can come with me, if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.83,0:54:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我有自己的承诺要信守\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have promises of my own to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.37,0:55:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那再见了 佩拉基尔领主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then mae glenno. Lord of Pelargir.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.12,0:55:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,南方
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.04,0:55:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,埃瑞吉安
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.37,0:55:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,奥克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Orc-treachery.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.91,0:55:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那条路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.79,0:55:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是通往...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gather it leads to--
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.04,0:55:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,埃瑞吉安 大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eregion, my liege.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.04,0:56:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来找索隆 却找到阿达尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We came in search of Sauron. And instead, we find Adar?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.83,0:56:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是一伙的还是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could they be in league with each other or...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.70,0:56:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可能在战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.91,0:56:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,奥克大军进军精灵王国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A legion of Orcs have marched into Elvish lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.37,0:56:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所有人都在战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are all of us at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.87,0:56:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们的大军前往魔多之前 要让至高王知道这消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Word of this must reach the High King before our host sails for Mordor.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.37,0:56:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.41,0:56:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.37,0:56:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的晚餐跑掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that's our supper gettin' away!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.50,0:56:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.95,0:56:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,归队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Back in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.20,0:56:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁 继续找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is it? Keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.66,0:56:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就在附近 继续找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're nearby. Keep lookin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.70,0:57:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁 那什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is it? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.08,0:57:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这边传来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Came from over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.37,0:57:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我闻到精灵的味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can smell an Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.45,0:57:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,太神奇了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.41,0:57:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,给我彻底找 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave no stone unturned. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.75,0:57:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,快去林顿 我会尽力拖延他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get to Lindon. I will occupy them as long as I am able.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.37,0:57:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,继续找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.20,0:57:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.08,0:57:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔隆德 拿去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it, Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.16,0:58:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.50,0:58:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.95,0:58:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I stand alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.37,0:58:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,砍下她的右手拇指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cut off her right thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.95,0:58:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快说其他的在哪 就留你左手拇指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell us where the others are, I'll let you keep the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.29,0:59:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她牺牲自己拯救我们大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She sacrificed herself to save us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.04,0:59:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你错了 坎尼尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you are mistaken, Camnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.70,0:59:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她这么做不是为了救我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She did not do it to save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.20,0:59:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.45,0:59:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了救戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She did it to save the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.87,0:59:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.58,0:59:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是精灵领地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These are Elven lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.37,0:59:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,滚回魔影去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go back to the shadow.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.33,1:00:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一颗星照耀着我们相遇的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A star shines on the hour of our meeting...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.58,1:00:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,加拉德瑞尔夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lady Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.08,1:00:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,歌声起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now let the song begin
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.79,1:00:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起唱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let us sing together
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.16,1:00:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,歌唱那太阳 星星 月亮与轻雾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of sun, stars, moon and mist,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.16,1:00:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,雨水与云天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rain and cloudy weather
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.87,1:00:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,唱那新芽上的阳光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Light on the budding leaf
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.58,1:00:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,羽毛上的露珠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dew on the feather
